HEADWORD: Appel
<hw>Ap`pel"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., prop., a
call. See <er>Appeal</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <fld>(Fencing)</fld>
<def>A tap or stamp of the foot as a warning of intent to attack; --
called also <altname>attack</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Appellable</ent>⟦br⟧
